    "description": "Students develop advanced woodworking skills in furniture design, millwork, and specialty projects. This course emphasizes project design and costing, industry-standard finishing, and professional woodworking practices for carpentry and furniture-making careers.",
    "general_description": "Advanced furniture and millwork, project design and costing, industry-standard finishing.",
